#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid "Misc Options"
msgstr "Razne opcije"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open folders in separate windows"
msgstr "Otvaraj fascikle u zasebnim prozorima"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:36
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If this option is checked, a new &konqueror; window will be created when "
#| "you open a folder, rather than simply showing that folder's contents in "
#| "the current window."
msgid ""
"If this option is checked, a new &konqueror; window will be created when you "
"open a folder, rather than simply showing that folder’s contents in the "
"current window."
msgstr ""
"Ako je ovo popunjeno, fascikle će biti otvarane u novom prozoru "
"<application>K‑osvajača</application>, umesto da sadržaj fascikle prosto "
"zameni onaj u tekućem prozoru."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:41
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Show 'Delete' menu entries which bypass the trashcan"
msgid "Show “Delete” menu entries which bypass the trashcan"
msgstr "Brisanje u menijima zaobilazi smeće"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:43
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Check this if you want <quote>Delete</quote> menu commands to be "
#| "displayed on the desktop and in the file manager's context menus. You can "
#| "always delete files by holding the &Shift; key while calling "
#| "<guimenuitem>Move to Trash</guimenuitem>."
msgid ""
"Check this if you want <quote>Delete</quote> menu commands to be displayed "
"on the desktop and in the file manager’s context menus. You can always "
"delete files by holding the &Shift; key while calling <guimenuitem>Move to "
"Trash</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"Popunite ovo ako želite da se u kontekstnim menijima površi i menadžera "
"fajlova daje naredba <guimenuitem>Obriši</guimenuitem>. Fajlove u svakom "
"slučaju može obrisati držanjem tastera <keycap>Shift</keycap> pri izboru "
"<guimenuitem>Premesti u smeće</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:48
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The settings for &konqueror;'s file manager mode on the <guilabel>View "
#| "Modes</guilabel>, <guilabel>Navigation</guilabel>, <guilabel>Services</"
#| "guilabel>, <guilabel>General</guilabel> and <guilabel>Trash</guilabel> "
#| "pages are used by &dolphin; as well."
msgid ""
"The settings for &konqueror;’s file manager mode on the <guilabel>View "
"Modes</guilabel>, <guilabel>Navigation</guilabel>, <guilabel>Services</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>General</guilabel> and <guilabel>Trash</guilabel> pages "
"are used by &dolphin; as well."
msgstr ""
"Postavke za <application>K‑osvajač</application> u režimu menadžera fajlova, "
"na stranicama <guilabel>Načini prikaza</guilabel>, <guilabel>Navigacija</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Servisi</guilabel>, <guilabel>Opšte</guilabel> i "
"<guilabel>Smeće</guilabel>, važe i u <application>Dolphinu</application>."
